headerBackgroundImage.name: headerBackgroundImage
headerBackgroundImage.prettyName: Banner (header image - the name of an image attached to the theme document)

logoImage.prettyName: Logo (image displayed at the top left corner of the header - the name of an image attached to the theme document; if set, it has priority over the logo configured in the skin and the default logo)

pageBackgroundPosition.name: pageBackgroundPosition
pageBackgroundPosition.prettyName: Page background image position and repeat (CSS syntax, for example: "left top repeat-x")

textPrimaryColor.name: textPrimaryColor
textPrimaryColor.prettyName: Informative text color (Modified by, Created by, etc)

textSecondaryColor.name: textSecondaryColor
textSecondaryColor.prettyName: Details text color (Comments date, attachments date, etc)
